# **Utilman Password Reset**
1ï¸âƒ£ Identify the Windows Partition
diskpart           # Launch Disk Management tool
list volume        # Show all partitions
exit               # Exit diskpart

2ï¸âƒ£ Backup utilman.exe
cd C:\Windows\System32                   # Navigate to System32 folder
ren utilman.exe utilman.exe.bak          # Rename Utilman to keep a backup

3ï¸âƒ£ Replace utilman.exe with CMD
copy C:\Windows\System32\cmd.exe C:\Windows\System32\utilman.exe  # Replace Utilman with CMD

4ï¸âƒ£ Change User Password
net user USERNAME NEWPASSWORD   # Change password for any user
net user Mahmoud 123456         # Example: Change password for user Mahmoud

5ï¸âƒ£ Restore Original utilman.exe
cd C:\Windows\System32
del utilman.exe
ren utilman.exe.bak utilman.exe  # Restore original Utilman
